#### Education

Residents of MCAS New River are zoned for schools administered by the [Department of Defense Education Activity](/Department_of_Defense_Education_Activity) (DoDEA). The sole educational institution located directly on the air station premises is Delalio Elementary School. For secondary education, students attend Brewster Middle School and [Lejeune High School](/Lejeune_High_School), both of which are situated within [Camp Lejeune](/Camp_Lejeune) and serve the broader community.

